doc.ContractDescription: IGF::OT::IGF CONTRACTOR STATEMENT OF RELEASE IN CONSIDERATION OF THE MODIFICATION(S) AGREED TO HEREIN AS COMPLETE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENTS FOR THE CONTRACTORS REVISED PROPOSAL DATED 10/28/16 FOR THE USAO OFFICE RENOVATIONS PROJECT, THE CONTRACTOR HEREBY RELEASES THE GOVERNMENT FROM ANY AND ALL LIABILITY UNDER THIS CONTRACT FOR FURTHER EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENTS ATTRIBUTABLE TO SUCH FACTS OR CIRCUMSTANCES GIVING RISE TO THE PROPOSAL(S) FOR ADJUSTMENT MODIFICATION PS02. THIS MODIFICATION INCREASES THE AMOUNT BY $3,025.00 FROM $67,045.42 TO MAKE THE TOTAL OF THE ENTIRE CONTRACT $70,070.42. THE INCREASE IS FOR AN ASBESTOS ABATEMENT SPECIFICATION WORK PLAN. THIS IS A CHANGE ORDER MODIFICATION OF THE PROJECT DESCRIBED PER THE ATTACHED SCOPE OF WORK, ORDER NUMBER GS-03-P-16-QK-7142. ALL OTHER TERMS AND CONDITIONS WILL REMAIN THE SAME. THE CONTRACT COMPLETION DATE WILL BE EXTENDED FROM DECEMBER 30, 2016 TO JANUARY 30, 2017. IT IS AGREED THAT THE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENT PROVIDED FOR IN THIS MODIFICATION CONSTITUTES AN ACCORD AND SATISFACTION OF ANY AND ALL PAST, PRESENT AND FUTURE CLAIMS FOR ADDITIONAL MONETARY COMPENSATION AND TIME FOR THE ACCOMPLISHMENT OF THE WORK DESCRIBED IN THIS MODIFICATION.
